title: Kendall Jenner records herself driving her car around
text:
She loves capturing just about every moment of her life for her Instagram followers, and that appears to include drives in her car.

Kendall Jenner recorded herself from behind the wheel on Tuesday.

The phone appeared to have been propped up on the dashboard as Kendall, 23, drove the car around.

Let's get this show on the road: Kendall Jenner recorded herself driving her car on Tuesday

The device was clearly hands-free, but Kendall still occasionally gazed at the phone while maneuvering the vehicle about.

Seatbelt strapped in, Kendall steered the car to and fro wearing a pretty butterfly filter over the cheeks.

The model did indeed look radiant for her drive.

The sunshine made Kendall's long brunette hair look extra glossy, while her complexion was accentuated with an edgy coat of smoky eye shadow.

Spreading her wings: The model wore a pretty butterfly filter for the drive

Busy bee: It's barely halfway through the week and already Kendall has been quite busy

It's barely halfway through the week and already Kendall has been quite busy.

The model and her sister Kylie Jenner dropped the fall 2019 collection of their joint fashion line on Tuesday.

In addition to the collection, Kendall attended her father Caitlyn Jenner's 70th birthday on Tuesday night alongside sisters Kim Kardashian, Kourtney, and Kylie Jenner.

Strike a pose: Jenner could not help but admire her appearance as she gazed towards the camera

The model headed to Nobu with her family to celebrate Caitlyn's big day at the Malibu restaurant.

And it won't be long until the family will be celebrating yet another big birthday.

Kendall will be ringing in her 24th birthday this Sunday.
